title: Index of Total Crop Production for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1862-1930 (2)--Original Data, 1866-1950. Source: G.F. Warren And F.A. Pearson, The Physical Volume Of Production In The United States, Table 1, P. 5. Data For 1931: Direct From F.A. Pearson. Data For 1932: Cornell University Agricultural Experiment Station Memoir 144, 1932.
